- DCR balance privacy_reward is higher-better: privacy_reward = 1 - abs(raw_dcr_real_closer_rate - 0.5).
- Treat raw_dcr_real_closer_rate and privacy_reward as one DCR balance signal; do not describe them as separate DCR changes.
- dcr_real/dcr_test quantiles are nearest-neighbor distances; larger distances reduce exact-neighbor risk, while raw DCR balance should stay near 0.5.

